{"tid":702934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(CCTVB) 《晚間新聞》收視不敵ViuTV《世界盃》","createTime":"2018-06-15T10:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T12:28:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d1bcfa49b75a25c353f2187ebaa22be2dfc8e9a9","tid":702934,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180615/58322155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58322155&d=YnwWlSBWHhr3D8QJ6eb0lNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a29ca24b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58322155&h=46079d99\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180615/58322155</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月15日<br />\n<br />\n【無綫慘敗】ViuTV直播世界盃揭幕戰 跨平台總收視逾100萬人次<br />\n<br />\n33,790<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0615 16:50<br />\n<br />\n四年一度體壇盛事「2018俄羅斯世界盃」噚晚開鑼，除咗NowTV獨家直播64場賽事外，免費電視ViuTV亦有得直播19場賽事，包括噚日主辦國俄羅斯對沙特阿拉伯嘅揭幕戰。<br />\n<br />\n噚晚場揭幕戰俄羅斯最終大勝沙特阿拉伯5比0，而據《蘋果》了解，ViuTV噚晚10點開始直播揭幕禮亦大勝對手無綫嘅《晚間新聞》。ViuTV噚晚錄得最高12點（每點觀眾人次65540，即約79萬人次），據知是近幾屆世界盃最高收視的一次。對戰的無綫11點《晚間新聞》，平均收視跌到得約52萬人次，最低更跌到46萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，ViuTV昨晚錄得平均10點收視，只係計電視直播，未計跨平台。計番ViuTV的Online收看人次有22萬，再加埋電視觀眾，即合共逾100萬人次收看。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，噚晚ViuTV由直播揭幕禮到揭幕戰，平均收視有10點，即約有72萬觀眾人次，收視大飈升，最高收視一度去到12點，大約有79萬人次收看。<br />\n<br />\nViuTV直播世界盃，無綫收視難免受影響。除劇集《飛虎之潛行極戰》「倖免於難」之外，之後播出的《食好D食平D》收視微跌2點，平均得番17點（111萬觀眾）。<br />\n<br />\n至於11點播嘅《晚間新聞》最慘情，對正世界盃開波，平均收視由之前12點（約79萬人次）狂瀉到只餘8點（約52萬人次）。其中頭15分鐘收視仍有10點（即約66萬人次），ViuTV就有11點（約72萬人次）；後15分鐘無綫得番7點收視，ViuTV就有12點。"},{"pid":"238ce70946acb643c8fde4c230148c696cfc298a","tid":702934,"uid":35221,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"CCTVB上上下下長病百歲、皇天擊殺、落地獄、立死全家"},{"pid":"1af9bb9f45483bc5d81d6fbb4584af0d6185b156","tid":702934,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c5e557fc2420667a28efb80997b70513fdb674","tid":702934,"uid":41508,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56a5613d5e7ab757aaf2f752bd28750137ecb657","tid":702934,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6c5e557fc2420667a28efb80997b70513fdb674","tid":702934,"uid":41508,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"24小時感激TBB有得免費播<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ab4bdd6890ed9be292c7e8767df5fda30422ef","tid":702934,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"[$8,000 問題]<br />\n昨晚間間茶餐廳部部電視機都長開播住既系：<br />\n<br />\nA. TVB 翡翠台<br />\nB. TVB 翡翠二台<br />\nC. TVB 翡翠新聞台<br />\nD. 熄機"},{"pid":"747cf24a11ebf9eefad1bf368239cc24b7ec9722","tid":702934,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18ab4bdd6890ed9be292c7e8767df5fda30422ef","tid":702934,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"[$8,000 問題]<br />\n昨晚間間茶餐廳部部電視機都長開播住既系：<br />\n<br />\nA. TVB 翡翠台<br />\nB. TVB 翡翠二台<br />\nC. TVB 翡翠新聞台<br />\nD. 熄機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"而家係慣性收視都救唔到《晚間新聞》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771b9350ee38cd53f23c431bd8c1a2de0b28e547","tid":702934,"uid":48973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6c5e557fc2420667a28efb80997b70513fdb674","tid":702934,"uid":41508,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:50:36.000Z","msg":"荷蘭lag"},{"pid":"6fb97cc76d215d3cc6710260d8cacb71865f